<p>I have a problem with sceditor. For example, I pasted to the editor text and made it bold, so html now looks like:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;strong&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet&lt;/strong&gt; </code></pre>  <p>Than I paste same text between ipsum and dolor and expect that all text will be in bold, but I get this when I switch to source view</p>  <pre><code>&lt;strong&gt;Lorem ipsum &lt;/strong&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet&lt;strong&gt;dolor sit amet&lt;/strong&gt; </code></pre>  <p>How to make ckeditor keep formatting for the inserted text, so html after pasting would look like </p>  <pre><code>&lt;strong&gt;Lorem ipsum Lorem ipsum dolor sit ametdolor sit amet&lt;/strong&gt; </code></pre>  <p>Maybe some config variables?</p>